      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776222039552,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5. Drivers need to report their progress during \nthe trip. We create a ride driver update endpoint \nthat takes the ride ID and a status like \n“picked up” or “dropped off”.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5. Drivers need to report their progress during \nthe trip. We create a ride driver update endpoint \nthat takes the ride ID and a status like \n“picked up” or “dropped off”.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
